channel.title: DEREGISTERED Players
channel.description:
Hi Im trying to start my own 2006 Remake for me and some friends to mess around on, logging on for the first time and creating a new account works, but logging onto an account again it just goes to a black screen and freezes. I think the problem has something to do with this... Server CMD Says This - [REGISTERED TO SITE]: Nate [REGISTERED]: Nate Game Saved for player Nate [DEREGISTERED]: Nate
If anyone knows what the problem is or how to fix if that would be great. Thanks.
